{
  "name": "w06_d09_01.ks",
  "lines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "line": "夏休みも、そろそろ後半。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041554\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "line": "「にいさ〜ん。こっち終わったよ〜」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "line": "洗い終えたボウルを手にして、弥恵がとたとたと\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "line": "近づいてくる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "line": "「おつかれさま、弥恵。えーっと、これで全部かな？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041555\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "line": "「うん。わざわざ来てもらってごめんね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "line": "「構わないさ。こっちも特に打ち合わせとかがあったわけ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "line": "　じゃないし」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "line": "お菓子作り同好会は普段どおり活動していたのだが、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "line": "アップルパイが急に忙しくなったらしく、呼び出しが\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "line": "かかってしまった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "line": "生徒会の仕事で俺と一緒に登校していたいずみ姉さんは\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "line": "帰ることになってしまって。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "line": "同好会の方も責任者として弥恵を残して、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "line": "みこと姉ちゃんと絵麻は店に戻ることになった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "line": "@Talk name=絵麻/心の声 voice=EM040129\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "line": "ただ、俺は絵麻に『お兄ちゃんはお姉ちゃんと一緒に\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "line": "お片付けをお願いします』と言われて、言われるがまま\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "line": "学校に残っていた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "line": "絵麻に弥恵との関係を気遣われるのは兄として、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "line": "とんでもなく恥ずかしいんだが……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "line": "まあ、どれだけ忙しくなったと言っても、父さんと母さん、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "line": "いずみ姉さんにみこと姉ちゃん、そして智花もいるんだ。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 98,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "line": "絵麻だって最近はみこと姉ちゃんの後ろに\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "line": "くっついたりして、フロアの仕事も頑張ってくれているし。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 103,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 104,
      "line": "今日はお言葉に甘えさせてもらおう。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 107,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 108,
      "line": "「そういえばどうだった？　ふたりのできばえは」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 114,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041556\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 115,
      "line": "「うん。絵麻ちゃんはすごく上手に焼けてるよ。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 116,
      "line": "　みこと姉さんはね……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 122,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041557\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 123,
      "line": "「あ〜。あはは……もうちょっとがんばらないと\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 124,
      "line": "　ダメかも……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 127,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 128,
      "line": "「そ、そうか……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 131,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 132,
      "line": "現在お菓子作り同好会では、クレープ作りの猛特訓が\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 133,
      "line": "繰り広げられていた。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 138,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 139,
      "line": "「おっかしいなぁ。パイ生地はあんなに上手に\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 140,
      "line": "　作れてたってのに」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 146,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041558\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 147,
      "line": "「う、うん。それはわたしもびっくりだったんだけど、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 148,
      "line": "　クレープ生地は薄いから……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 153,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041559\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 154,
      "line": "「パイ生地はクレープに比べたらぶ厚いし、ちょっと\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 155,
      "line": "　固いから力もいるし」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 161,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041560\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 162,
      "line": "「だから、みこと姉さんの力加減にちょうど\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 163,
      "line": "　合ってたのかなって」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 166,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 167,
      "line": "「つまり、みこと姉ちゃんがパイ生地で絵麻がフィリングっ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 168,
      "line": "　ていうアップルパイの役割分担が奇跡だったってことか」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 174,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041561\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 175,
      "line": "「あはは。でも、感覚をつかめばすぐだと思うから」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 180,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 181,
      "line": "会話をしながら弥恵はてきぱきと台ふきを手洗いし、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 182,
      "line": "調理台の上に広げていく。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 185,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 186,
      "line": "ここの厨房にも慣れてきたみたいで、日に日に手際が\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 187,
      "line": "良くなってきているのが俺にもよく分かる。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 193,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041562\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 194,
      "line": "「ふぇ？　な、なぁに、兄さん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 197,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 198,
      "line": "「ううん。なんでもない」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 204,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041563\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 205,
      "line": "「なんでもなくないよぉ〜。兄さん、なにか言いたそうな\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 206,
      "line": "　顔してた〜」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 209,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 210,
      "line": "「はは、そんなことないって」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 213,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 214,
      "line": "弥恵がリラックスして、素を見せてくれる空間が学校にも\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 215,
      "line": "出来たということは、兄としてとても嬉しかった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 218,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 219,
      "line": "いや。恋人としても、かもな。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 222,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 223,
      "line": "だって、こんなに可愛い顔が見られるんだから。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 234,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 235,
      "line": "「それにしても、夏休みもあっという間だよな。もう\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 236,
      "line": "　半分以上過ぎちゃったし」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 242,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041564\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 243,
      "line": "「うん。そうだね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 249,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041565\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 250,
      "line": "「ぁ……でも、わたしは逆かも」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 253,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 254,
      "line": "「逆って？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 259,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041566\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 260,
      "line": "「その、夏休みってこんなに長かったんだっけって、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 261,
      "line": "　思っちゃってるかも」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 264,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 265,
      "line": "「へぇ……？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 271,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041567\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 272,
      "line": "「うん、なんでだろう。今までそんな風に思ったこと、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 273,
      "line": "　ないんだけどなぁ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 276,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 277,
      "line": "「ひょっとして、二学期になって学食でプリンを\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 278,
      "line": "　披露するのが待ちきれない、とか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 284,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041568\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 285,
      "line": "「そ、そうなのかな……？　はぅぅ、自分じゃ\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 286,
      "line": "　よくわからないよぉ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 289,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 290,
      "line": "「そっか。あー、でも、そうなると俺はちょっぴり\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 291,
      "line": "　寂しいかもな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 296,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041569\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 297,
      "line": "「え？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 300,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 301,
      "line": "「だって、まだ俺とあと数人しか知らない弥恵のプリンが、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 302,
      "line": "　学校中の生徒に知られちゃうんだもん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 305,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 306,
      "line": "「弥恵の頑張りが認められるわけだから、もちろんそれは\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 307,
      "line": "　嬉しいことなんだけど、なんだかさ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 313,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041570\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 314,
      "line": "「兄さん……はぅぅぅ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 320,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041571\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 321,
      "line": "「じゃ、じゃあわたしっ、プリンのレシピ変えるっ。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 322,
      "line": "　それと新しく、兄さんだけが知ってるプリンも作るよっ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 325,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 326,
      "line": "「はは、そんなことしなくてもいいって。ごめんごめん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 329,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 330,
      "line": "「ちょっと弥恵をひとりじめしたかっただけなんだ」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 336,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041572\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 337,
      "line": "「ふぁぁっ、ひ、ひとりじめ！？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 340,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 341,
      "line": "「うん。そりゃそうだろ？　いつも考えてるよ、俺。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 342,
      "line": "　弥恵をひとりじめしたいなって」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 349,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041573\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 350,
      "line": "「いいっ、いつもなのっ！？　はぅぅ〜」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 353,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 354,
      "line": "「うん。いつも」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 362,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041574\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 363,
      "line": "「ぁっ。ふぁぁ……にいさぁん……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 366,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 367,
      "line": "火が出そうなくらい顔を赤くして恥ずかしがる弥恵が\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 368,
      "line": "あまりに可愛くて、ついつい抱きしめてしまう。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 371,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 372,
      "line": "「ほんと、静かだな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 378,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041575\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 379,
      "line": "「う、うん……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 382,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 383,
      "line": "遠くでは運動部たちのかけ声が時々響いているものの、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 384,
      "line": "校舎の中はしんと静まりかえっている。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 387,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 388,
      "line": "「考えてみたら、ここに弥恵と俺だけしかいないって\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 389,
      "line": "　いうのも、珍しい気がする」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 394,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041576\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 395,
      "line": "「そうだね。おばさん達だったり、岡野先生だったり……\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 396,
      "line": "　ここはいつも賑やかだったよね」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 402,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041577\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 403,
      "line": "「でも、今日は誰も来ないよ。夏休みだもん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 406,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 407,
      "line": "「そうだな」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 412,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041578\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 413,
      "line": "「うん。兄さん……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 419,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041579\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 420,
      "line": "「んふ……すぅぅ……んふふ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 425,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 426,
      "line": "「弥恵？　わわっ……」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 429,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 430,
      "line": "すっと俺の胸元に顔をうずめて、弥恵が深く息を吸いこむ。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 433,
      "line": "@Talk name=心の声\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 434,
      "line": "鎖骨のあたりが少しひんやりとして、ぞくりとする感覚が\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 435,
      "line": "背中へ抜けていった。\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 441,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041580\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 442,
      "line": "「えへへ。兄さんのにおい、もらっちゃった」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 445,
      "line": "@Talk name=和哉\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 446,
      "line": "「汗くさくなかったか？」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 452,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041581\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 453,
      "line": "「ううん、全然そんなことないよ。兄さんのにおい、\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 454,
      "line": "　大好きだもん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 460,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041582\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 461,
      "line": "「……ぁ……あのね？　兄さん」\r\n"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 466,
      "line": "@Talk name=弥恵 voice=YE041583\r\n"
    },
    {
